‘You aren’t going to change things or say everything you want because he has his own habits, his own way of doing things, and I don’t think it would be wise to all of a sudden come up with some very different thing. There is a difference for sure, a huge difference between men’s and women’s tennis. I noticed it, I lived it as a player. I see it around.’

While the intention has always been for this to be a long-term arrangement, she did not want to project into the future yet.

‘Now I am in the moment, it is good fun, it is going well. We will see if it goes further or not. Regardless if it does, it is a great experience.’

